  24 Sep 2007; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> vhdl-mode-3.33.8.ebuild,
  vhdl-mode-3.33.21.ebuild:
  Drop dependency on cedet since the package also works without the speedbar.

*vhdl-mode-3.33.21 (23 Sep 2007)

  23 Sep 2007; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org>
  +files/vhdl-mode-info-dir-gentoo.patch, vhdl-mode-3.33.2.ebuild,
  -vhdl-mode-3.33.3.ebuild, vhdl-mode-3.33.8.ebuild,
  +vhdl-mode-3.33.21.ebuild:
  Version bump. Remove dependency on app-emacs/speedbar; update HOMEPAGE and
  SRC_URI; install Info file and documentation. Drop ~ppc-macos keyword.
  Remove old version.

  04 Jul 2007; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
